ities\n\n \n\n \n Our services\n\n At G3-Biz, we don't just distribute Guinness products\n\n we empower businesses to succeed. Here's how: \n\n More Services \n \n \n Reputable Customer of GCSA\n\n G3-Biz is the main distributor of GCSA products in Limbe Cameroon. Consultation services are additional support that G3-Biz offers to its customers free of charge, ensuring you get the most out of your partnership with us...\n\n Team Spotlight:\n\n The Dream Team Behind Our Success\n\n More Team Members \n \n \n MANAGING DIRECTOR/BUSINESS CONSULTANT\n\n Moses Fongang Kem\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n DEPOT MANAGER\n\n Therese Tayimfor\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n HOD HUMAN RESOURCE AND ADMINISTRATION\n\n Constance Njumanuh A.\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n HOD BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT\n\n Herman Ache Ayiseh\n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n View More...\n \n Depot\n\n Products\n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n News & Events\n\n Latest news\n\n \n \n \n 20 Mar, 25\n \n G3-Biz Ltd \n 0 Comments \n \n DIAGEO WOLD CLASS WAYS OF SELLING (DWWS)\n\n \n \n \n \n 13 Nov, 24\n \n G3-Biz Ltd \n 0 Comments \n \n Seeking IT Expert to Enhance the Skills of Our IT Officer for Improved Digital and Technical Support\n\n \n \n \n \n 25 Sep, 24\n \n G3-Biz Ltd \n 0 Comments \n \n 🌟 Women Crush Wednesday: Celebrating Mme Tayimfor Therese! 🌟\n\n \n \n Read More...\n \n \n Moses Fongang\n Quotes \n \n\n \n \n Work harder and make more money \n\n Moses Fongang\n \n \n \n 100% focus on compliance \n\n Moses Fongang\n \n \n \n Be creative and innovative \n\n Moses Fongang\n \n \n \n Take responsibility \n\n Moses Fongang\n \n Contact us for services\n\n +237 6 53 55 25 62\n info@g3-bizltd.com\n Mile 2 Limbe Cameroon\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nΔ",
